descriptionHTML:
VITTMM is a designer watchface app for Android Wear devices. Time is an intersection. V stands for hours I marks minutes. App has a nine colors customization and works in ambient mode. Have a nice TTMM.

Compatible with Huawei Watch, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch 3

Idea & design : Albert Salamon
Android programming : Michał Żyliński
